{"tid":231103,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲係出黎做野先養狗？","createTime":"2017-05-05T20:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T04:48:41.000Z","uid":39153,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20ff5224d9c2355cce85482f4c853c5c31c52038","tid":231103,"uid":39153,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T20:13:22.000Z","msg":"就黎畢業，計劃養狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屋企人無養開寵物，但都幾喜歡狗。<br />\n家母怕會臭，老豆無乜意見。<br />\n<br />\n但住緊既屋苑唔比養狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知點好<br />\n平時有做開運動，附近都有地方帶狗散步既，<br />\n比較多時間獨處，主要都係自己負責番家務<br />\n一直想養隻狗會無咁孤單，但就想自己負責番養佢既洗費等等<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲有類似既情況，或者分享下啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講下屋企人點睇？佔空間幾大？洗費等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7fecb22202677a4222a67171bfd5d7874e82633","tid":231103,"uid":62337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T20:16:08.000Z","msg":"家母怕臭，屋苑唔俾養，仲有選擇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa62b05922d0f95950adb09e7ecb06f08e626fe7","tid":231103,"uid":39153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T20:19:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>家母怕臭，屋苑唔俾養，仲有選擇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見過有住客用袋住落街先放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家母無乜時間起屋企"},{"pid":"d9a076617d854a37d20d9bfcedeab5e625408948","tid":231103,"uid":105207,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T20:20:04.000Z","msg":"記得以領養代替購買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8573a20520fb64fa4233153570de8224c4c62bc6","tid":231103,"uid":111771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T23:32:48.000Z","msg":"建議你可以玩住尼奧寵物先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace815cf86a3de4433140a460884b36138f36d2e","tid":231103,"uid":57840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:39:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>家母怕臭，屋苑唔俾養，仲有選擇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見過有住客用袋住落街先放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家母無乜時間起屋企</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔俾就咪搞啦<br />\n一陣人地投訴你隻狗你冇得唔養"},{"pid":"7ec2e43cd44d632a119ffcbcac1fa6b64bf6421c","tid":231103,"uid":55045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:54:55.000Z","msg":"屋苑唔俾養 就咩都唔洗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d19ba3f298b28d09ef824f2334a77988d149c4","tid":231103,"uid":61359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:26:39.000Z","msg":"俾人投訴係咪做定準備會搬走？"},{"pid":"307760d4d653c6491fec017d70cc70fcad998533","tid":231103,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T06:40:16.000Z","msg":"其實公屋都大把人養狗，只要自律，做好清潔同埋隻狗唔會成日吠就唔係問題。<br />\n<br />\n不過養寵物好大責任，而且又要帶狗狗散步，散完步教要清潔，建議你出黎做左野一排先，確定你放左工之後仲有心情力氣去照顧狗狗先再諗。"},{"pid":"204553f32e6dbc554199a373ba9bc163390cb41d","tid":231103,"uid":21654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T07:56:56.000Z","msg":"睇你應該會去買狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連愛協咁低門檻都要指明住嘅地方比養先得"},{"pid":"ca2b7753777e583f5666d8747939d39927f2fa6e","tid":231103,"uid":12219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:02:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>家母怕臭，屋苑唔俾養，仲有選擇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見過有住客用袋住落街先放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家母無乜時間起屋企</blockquote><br />\n我男朋友就係，最近先養同佢自己負責返d洗費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你家母冇咩時間係屋企，而你遲d要返工既時候邊個睇住隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢bb個時一日食三餐你餵到佢？<br />\n同埋你仲要教佢好多野，有好多野屋企人都要配合<br />\n建議你諗清楚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42638f911e1c9ea4abf016642459f650813b15e0","tid":231103,"uid":71462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:20:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你應該會去買狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連愛協咁低門檻都要指明住嘅地方比養先得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者係facebook群組領養"},{"pid":"f4adb15beaa0a7fb69006cd4ae240a24b711aa71","tid":231103,"uid":93139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:24:12.000Z","msg":"你住個到唔比養 就唔好養啦 唔好害左隻狗 <br />\n養狗唔會係你想像中就易"},{"pid":"164b3e74d57fbc647c4ca66232861a3f8644a7b5","tid":231103,"uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:27:58.000Z","msg":"住個度唔比養真係唔駛諗<br />\n香港人最鐘意玩投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d80cd7f7faa81be8d6038c42a716ab329b15ff6","tid":231103,"uid":39153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:23:56.000Z","msg":"除左村屋真係無乜屋苑比養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日先見有個呀叔大搖大擺拖隻狗入大堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有絲打講到邊個照顧隻狗既問題，值得正視，<br />\n出到黎做野穩定左個工時先好諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e04a2129efd00671e5f8a94b4f935000bb0391c","tid":231103,"uid":20256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:29:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左村屋真係無乜屋苑比養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日先見有個呀叔大搖大擺拖隻狗入大堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有絲打講到邊個照顧隻狗既問題，值得正視，<br />\n出到黎做野穩定左個工時先好諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果有人投訴你會搬屋定棄養？<br />\n如果你鄰居係因為驚狗而搬入黎呢<br />\n一句講哂 咪撚咁自私啦"},{"pid":"9adaeeb1777cf8512924c41f72c24a16a9307803","tid":231103,"uid":19542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:39:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>除左村屋真係無乜屋苑比養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日先見有個呀叔大搖大擺拖隻狗入大堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有絲打講到邊個照顧隻狗既問題，值得正視，<br />\n出到黎做野穩定左個工時先好諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果有人投訴你會搬屋定棄養？<br />\n如果你鄰居係因為驚狗而搬入黎呢<br />\n一句講哂 咪撚咁自私啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係 唔俾養就唔好養啦"},{"pid":"f7c51ddcfed789a43af01bf7e933d725ca75b6cb","tid":231103,"uid":218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:42:48.000Z","msg":"搬咗去養得狗嘅地方先好養<br />\n人哋犯規唔代表你都可以跟住犯<br />\n佢畀人捉只係遲早問題<br />\n越嚟越多人養狗<br />\n萬一你啲鄰居頂唔順集體投訴 <br />\n咁你點處置隻狗？"},{"pid":"23a59ea782d927fe42c3ed553d716eb8bb6d6889","tid":231103,"uid":81508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T20:33:18.000Z","msg":"同男友講好左過兩年結婚就養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d37d9b9bfa1396d7c8f33ad63eaacf6db4fd57b","tid":231103,"uid":39153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"利申番，無講過唔搬就養/搬就養，亦無講過買狗定領養<br />\n<br />\n起曬杆做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c081035e43d46784997f7a9a08c54e232af83903","tid":231103,"uid":98,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"樓主呢啲人真係好撚自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff68293a5ab63bfeaaceb251616192a0c96549d","tid":231103,"uid":39153,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T15:12:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主呢啲人真係好撚自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點介定叫自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問緊意見同分享咁都有野批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c3716046af7c58dca2e50dc8935b1b2d0ee6df","tid":231103,"uid":16270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T20:15:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主呢啲人真係好撚自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點介定叫自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問緊意見同分享咁都有野批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你都擺明講緊想養 仲想頂咀"},{"pid":"a1fe471afd5ac26840b57c46c0f96db7f3a22b7a","tid":231103,"uid":56043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T21:26:28.000Z","msg":"建議去HKDR領養，細狗難啲比人投訴<br />\n但係你要負責任，唔好領養完又送番去hkdr <br />\n隻狗好撚sad <br />\n<br />\n利申： HKDR 義工"},{"pid":"2560680ec0625281ec576ab4d3e583d813fa4eeb","tid":231103,"uid":49131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T22:02:22.000Z","msg":"住果到唔比養 你自己都識講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一係你就唔好養 一係就搬去可以養既地方 人地起哂鋼唔係因為領養定購買既問題 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係你住果到唔比養啊！</span></span> 到時比人投訴人地要你一係棄養一係搬 你又想上黎問人攞意見？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}